WEBVTT

00:01.588 --> 00:06.034
Curacao is an island paradise nestled between Aruba and Bonaire.

00:06.355 --> 00:08.426
Easy to reach with daily direct flights...

00:08.515 --> 00:11.081
...from the US, Europe, and South America.

00:11.565 --> 00:13.995
Here, the skies are tranquil and placid.

00:14.506 --> 00:16.542
The seas are crystalline and warm.

00:17.098 --> 00:19.169
Located outside the Hurricane Belt,...

00:19.435 --> 00:22.718
...the island enjoys favorable weather virtually year-round.

00:23.103 --> 00:27.079
The capital, Willemstad, offers the ambiance of a cosmopolitan...

00:27.156 --> 00:31.252
...European city with a breathtaking beauty of an island locale.

00:32.220 --> 00:35.917
You'll see constant reminders everywhere of the Dutch, African...

00:36.083 --> 00:40.038
...and Latin people that combine to create one of the most interesting...

00:40.091 --> 00:41.488
...cultures in the Caribbean.

